UID:event_313517773@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260312T160927Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260316T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260316T200000
SUMMARY:Monday Night Trails in NW
DESCRIPTION:Portland Running Co. Weekly Group Runs\nJoin us for a Monday evening trail run in Forest Park\, followed by refreshments at Run Pub. Meet at 6 PM at PRC\, 2258 NW Raleigh St. in Portland. We'll embark from the store. Expect hills\, dirt\, and routes of 5–9 miles. All are welcome!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-running-co-weekly-group-runs/events/313517773/
